README for trinity-cursor-theme


CONFIGURATION
=============

  Add the following line to ~/.Xresources:

    Xcursor.theme: Trinity-Cursor-Theme

  Then, run xrdb -load ~/.Xresources and restart your WM.

  Or, there is the 2nd way:

  Create ~/.icons/default/index.theme with the following content:

    [Icon Theme]
    Name=Default
    Comment=Default Cursor Theme
    Inherits=Trinity-Cursor-Theme

  And restart your WM.


End of file.
